{
  "stem": "3524.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at about that time the invasion of Europe was beginning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they had decided to disband the Army Specialized Training Program, or ASTP as we called it at that time, and disperse the troops to active units.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My particular group was sent out to join the 104th infantry division in Camp Carson, Colorado.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that particular time, going on a train to Camp Carson, I developed the mumps with about 40 other fellows.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were hospitalized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was the minute we got there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By the time I got out of the hospital, they were making up a list of personnel who would be able to start this 104th-- or 120th Evacuation Hospital.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And because I had had some pharmacy training, I think my name was selected, and perhaps also because I wasn't available for active training at that time; they-- I'm sure the military commanders felt this was a good person to put on that list.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I recall, it was in March.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a new unit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we got there, they had a-- just the bare minimum corps of cadre, and they were just beginning the table of organization to fill the cadre and then the routine trainees.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were probably the second group to come in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Colonel Williams was our commander at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a lieutenant colonel-- medical officer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was told he was regular army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the regular army are those who make a career of the service.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the reserve corps are those that act as-- don't make a career of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They basically are civilians who serve in time of need.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never noticed it particularly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think during the war time, everybody worked together quite well.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
